rows.label: qst201819_msg0001
rows.name:
I think it's so cool you can talk to
Phonexes, Uka! I can't tell you how
jealous I am...

rows.label: qst201819_msg0002
rows.name:
Man, I wish I could talk to Phonexes...
I'm jealous, Uka!

rows.label: qst201819_msg0003
rows.name:
I would very much like to speak with
a Phonex one day. I envy you, Uka.

rows.label: qst201819_msg0004
rows.name:
Man, why can't I talk to Phonexes...?
I've got serious envy right now, Uka!

rows.label: qst201819_msg0005
rows.name:
Is that right?
We don't really talk about
anything special, though.

rows.label: qst201819_msg0006
rows.name:
Just day-to-day stuff,
or what's good to eat...

rows.label: qst201819_msg0007
rows.name:
Pretty much the same stuff everyone
talks about, you know?

rows.label: qst201819_msg0008
rows.name: But if you really insist, Rex-san...

rows.label: qst201819_msg0015
rows.name: But if you really insist, Nia-san...

rows.label: qst201819_msg0017
rows.name: But if you really insist, Zeke-san...

rows.label: qst201819_msg0016
rows.name: But if you really insist, Meleph-san...

rows.label: qst201819_msg0009
rows.name:
I can teach you some Phonex!
How about that?

rows.label: qst201819_msg0010
rows.name:
Really?
Yes please!

rows.label: qst201819_msg0011
rows.name:
Are you serious?
No backsies, yeah?

rows.label: qst201819_msg0012
rows.name:
That is a welcome offer.
I will take you up on it when
there is time to spare.

rows.label: qst201819_msg0013
rows.name:
What, seriously?
This is my lucky day!

rows.label: qst201819_msg0014
rows.name:
Yes!
It'll be our little project, Rex-san!

rows.label: qst201819_msg0018
rows.name:
Yes!
It'll be our little project, Nia-san!

rows.label: qst201819_msg0019
rows.name:
Yes!
It'll be our little project, Zeke-san!

rows.label: qst201819_msg0020
rows.name:
Yes!
It'll be our little project, Meleph-san!
